NK014(pha)003:0: dpal gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i sgrub thabs khrag 'thung mngon rdzogs bzhugs /
NK014(pha)003:1: dpal gsang ba'i snying po sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i sgrub
NK014(pha)003:2: thabs khrag 'thung mngon rdzogs zhes bya ba spyi dpal
NK014(pha)003:4: shin tu zhi ba dam pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK014(pha)003:5: gdug can gshed du gar dgus dpa' ba'i nyams //
NK014(pha)003:6: rdo rje mngon spyod rol pa'i phrin las can //
NK014(pha)003:7: khrag 'thung 'dus pa'i bdag nyid la phyag 'tshal //
NK014(pha)003:13: dbang sgrub chen mo dang 'brel na sa'i cho ga
NK014(pha)003:14: nas bzung rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor 'du bya ba'i
NK014(pha)003:15: las rim dkyil chog ltar shes par byas nas /
NK014(pha)003:16: gnyis pa cho ga'i sngon 'gro la rnam grangs brgyad las /
NK014(pha)003:17: dang po skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:19: bde gshegs yongs rdzogs dkon mchog gsum gyi ngang //
NK014(pha)003:20: dpal chen 'dus pa'i ngo bor yongs shar ba //
NK014(pha)003:21: spro bsdu'i byed po byang chub sems kyi lhar //
NK014(pha)003:22: rang ngo shes pa'i ngang nas skyabs su mchi //
NK014(pha)003:26: chos kyi dbyings la phyogs ris mnyam brdal yang //
NK014(pha)003:27: ma rtogs 'khrul par 'khyams pa'i bdag 'dzin bdud //
NK014(pha)003:28: 'od gsal chos sku'i klong du bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:29: dpal chen lha tshogs bsgrub par sems bskyed do //
NK014(pha)003:33: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK014(pha)003:34: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)003:35: mchog gsum bstan pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK014(pha)003:36: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK014(pha)003:37: dngos 'byor yid gyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:38: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:39: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK014(pha)003:40: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK014(pha)003:41: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK014(pha)003:42: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK014(pha)003:43: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK014(pha)003:44: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK014(pha)003:45: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK014(pha)003:46: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK014(pha)003:47: tshe rabs bgrangs ba'i las rnams kun //
NK014(pha)003:48: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK014(pha)003:49: bzhi pa bgegs gtor gtong ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:51: nga ni spyi dpal chen po ste //
NK014(pha)003:52: byang chub bsgrub la bar gcod pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:54: gtor ma longs la phyir dengs shig /
NK014(pha)003:55: gal te bka' las 'da' byed na //
NK014(pha)003:56: mgo bo tshal pa brgyar khos shing //
NK014(pha)003:57: lus ni rdul phran bzhin du bshig /
NK014(pha)003:58: h'u bzhi'i drag sngags dang thun brdeg /
NK014(pha)003:59: lnga pa mtshams gcod srung 'khor ni /
NK014(pha)003:61: bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje yi //
NK014(pha)003:62: spyan mig nyi zlas gzir zhing bsreg /
NK014(pha)003:63: thugs las khro bo'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK014(pha)003:64: stong gsum sprul pa'i me yis 'gengs //
NK014(pha)003:65: phyogs mtshams mtshon cha 'chol bas gtam sa //
NK014(pha)003:66: bdag med stong par mtshams gcad do //
NK014(pha)003:67: s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la ram ram tsakra
NK014(pha)003:68: warti ma h+aa kro ta sarba dush+tam e h'u phata
NK014(pha)003:69: / drug pa brda sgo dbye zhing brda phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK014(pha)003:70: nongs bshags dam bca' gzung ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:72: ma rig ling tog ye shes thur mas dbye //
NK014(pha)003:73: sems nyid lha skur rtogs pa'i brda' phyag 'tshal //
NK014(pha)003:74: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa chos sku'i klong du bshags //
NK014(pha)003:75: dpal chen srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ngo //
NK014(pha)003:77: dgu pa snod bcud byin 'bebs ni /
NK014(pha)003:79: dpal chen 'dus pa'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK014(pha)003:80: chos sku'i klong nas thugs rje bskyed //
NK014(pha)003:81: longs sku'i rnam rol cir yang bsgyur //
NK014(pha)003:82: sprul sku'i dkyil 'khor brten par bcas //
NK014(pha)003:83: dbang bskur byin phob rtags mtshan ston //
NK014(pha)003:84: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)003:85: sarba sa ma ya a be sha ya pheem pheem /
NK014(pha)003:86: brgyad pa mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:88: bdag nyid lhar gsal thugs ka'i h'u yig las //
NK014(pha)003:89: ram yam kham 'phros ye shes me rlung chus //
NK014(pha)003:90: mchod rdzas dngos 'dzin skyon sbyangs stong pa'i ngang //
NK014(pha)003:91: +aahls stong gsum b+han+d+hara rdzogs pa'i nang //
NK014(pha)003:92: 'khor 'das bcud drangs h'u las nyer spyod kyi //
NK014(pha)003:93: dam rdzas 'dod yon sprin phung rgya mtshor gyur //
NK014(pha)003:94: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya dang /
NK014(pha)003:95: badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+hu /
NK014(pha)003:99: rdo rje zhabs bsil ma la sogs pa mchod pa'i lha mos nam mkha' gang bar gyur /
NK014(pha)003:101: stong pa'i ngang las kam yig yongs gyur las //
NK014(pha)003:102: mi mgo'i sgyed steng a las b+han+d+ha'i nang //
NK014(pha)003:103: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte bar bcas pa'i dbus //
NK014(pha)003:104: go ku da ha na las sha lnga dang //
NK014(pha)003:105: bi mu ma ra sh+au las bdud rtsi lnga //
NK014(pha)003:106: rang rang sa bon gyis mtshan yam ram las //
NK014(pha)003:107: rlung g.yos me sbar dam rdzas zhu ba'i steng //
NK014(pha)003:108: h'u +amo s+w+aa am h+aa las phyag mtshan lnga //
NK014(pha)003:109: so sos yu ba byas pa'i dril bu rnams //
NK014(pha)003:110: yongs gyur rigs lnga yab yum mnyam sbyor gyur //
NK014(pha)003:111: h'u t+r+aam h+r+ai ah m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK014(pha)003:112: zla ba'i kha gcod sna tshogs rdo rje'i lter //
NK014(pha)003:113: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin //
NK014(pha)003:114: grwa bzhir yum bzhi rdo rje'i tog gi dbus //
NK014(pha)003:115: stangs dpyal kun gyi bde ba'i 'od rlangs sprin //
NK014(pha)003:116: dbyangs gsal las gyur 'bru gsum brtsegs ma yi //
NK014(pha)003:117: 'od kyis rgyal ba mchod cing gzhan don byas //
NK014(pha)003:118: tshur 'dus dam tshig rdzas dang dbyer med 'dris //
NK014(pha)003:119: ye shes bdud brtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur //
NK014(pha)003:120: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum du gsal bas bdud rtsi dkrugs shing /
NK014(pha)003:121: +aah h'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aah nyer gcig dang /
NK014(pha)003:125: stong pa'i ngang las gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod //
NK014(pha)003:126: gtor rdzas mchog chen mi dang seng+ge glang //
NK014(pha)003:127: ba lang rta sha bdud rtsi lnga yi steng //
NK014(pha)003:128: rigs lnga yab yum phyag mtshan rnams kyis mtshan //
NK014(pha)003:129: 'og nas rlung g.yos me sbar bdud rtsi khol //
NK014(pha)003:130: zag med ro brgya ldan pa'i gtor ma ni //
NK014(pha)003:131: dbang po drug la dgyes dgu'i sprin du gyur //
NK014(pha)003:132: +aahmh'u ma h+aa b+ha ling+ta te dz+wa ba ling ta
NK014(pha)003:133: ba la b+aa te gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK014(pha)003:136: +aahls yum mkha' rnam thar sum ldan dbyings //
NK014(pha)003:137: ma las nyi dkyil ra yig yongs gyur las //
NK014(pha)003:138: chags chen srid pa'i rak+ta 'bar ba'i klong //
NK014(pha)003:139: ngar 'dzin r+au tra'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad rnams //
NK014(pha)003:140: thabs mchog rdo rje nor bus sbyangs pa yis //
NK014(pha)003:141: 'khor ba lugs ldog skye med chos skur bsgral //
NK014(pha)003:142: zegs ma'i tshogs la zhing gi lhu dam dang //
NK014(pha)003:143: rdo rje sgeg mo'i mchod sprin spro bar gyur //
NK014(pha)003:144: +aahmh'u ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+ai th+aah lan gsum /
NK014(pha)003:145: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis /
NK014(pha)003:146: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:147: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i las kyi rim pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:149: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:150: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa gnyis kyi dang po la'ang nang gses rnam grangs brgyad las /
NK014(pha)003:151: dang po de bzhin nyid gyi teng nge 'dzin ni /
NK014(pha)003:152: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pas //
NK014(pha)003:153: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK014(pha)003:154: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK014(pha)003:155: de phyir dngos po med pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:156: lus dang ngag sems chos thams cad //
NK014(pha)003:157: gang na'ang ma gnas mi dmigs pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:158: rang bzhin mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK014(pha)003:159: mig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis //
NK014(pha)003:160: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK014(pha)003:161: gnyis pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK014(pha)003:162: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad la //
NK014(pha)003:163: snying rje chen pos kun tu khyab //
NK014(pha)003:164: rang byung de nyid dngos med par //
NK014(pha)003:165: kun gyi phyag rgya'i rgyu yin no //
NK014(pha)003:166: gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK014(pha)003:167: sngon po h'u nyid he ru'i dngos //
NK014(pha)003:168: nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK014(pha)003:169: de las dpal chen he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:170: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu yi //
NK014(pha)003:171: 'jigs pa yi ni dus ltar grag /
NK014(pha)003:172: bzhi pa rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:173: rgyu'i he ru ka sku mdog smug nag rdo rje
NK014(pha)003:174: dang dung khrag 'dzin pa'i thugs ka nas e yam
NK014(pha)003:175: ram sum kem ram rnams chad /
NK014(pha)003:176: e las nam mkha' mthing nag /
NK014(pha)003:179: sum las zhing chen gyi sa gzhi /
NK014(pha)003:180: kem las rus pa'i ri rab /
NK014(pha)003:181: ram las me'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK014(pha)003:182: rgyu'i he ru ka'i thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad /
NK014(pha)003:185: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)003:186: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)003:187: phyogs bcur rgya yang ma chad pa //
NK014(pha)003:188: phyi dang nang med kun tu snang //
NK014(pha)003:190: gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK014(pha)003:191: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK014(pha)003:193: ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK014(pha)003:194: gzhal yas khang rnam thar bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags
NK014(pha)003:196: phyi nang nyis rim 'bar ba'i khyams gnyis dang ldan pa'i phyi ma'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang /
NK014(pha)003:197: nang rtsig rim pa gsum pa /
NK014(pha)003:198: gnyis ka'ang thod pa skam rnyid rlon gsum khrag zhag
NK014(pha)003:199: gi 'dam gyis brtsigs shing gnam lcags ur mo'i gzer
NK014(pha)003:200: gyis bltams pa'i steng na thod pa sna tshogs pas
NK014(pha)003:201: bkra ba'i pha gu 'phyar thabs su bkod pa las
NK014(pha)003:202: rgyu ma dang don snying gi mgul 'khor 'phyang ba
NK014(pha)003:203: / de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la
NK014(pha)003:204: ma ka ra'i kha nas sbrul sgram dang thod skam
NK014(pha)003:205: gyi d+r+wa ba dang dra ba phyed pa /
NK014(pha)003:206: don snying dang yan lag gi 'phyang 'phrul /
NK014(pha)003:208: lcang lo'i rda yab dang dril g.yer rlung gis skyod pas mdzes shing /
NK014(pha)003:209: phyi ngos su bya 'dabs las 'phyang ba'i rkang lag gi shar bu /
NK014(pha)003:210: steng ngos su sgal tshigs kyi mda' yab tshar du dang ra ba /
NK014(pha)003:211: de dag gi bar bar du zhing chen gyi gdugs /
NK014(pha)003:214: zhing lpags kyi lhab lhub sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs pas bkra ba /
NK014(pha)003:215: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i phyi 'gram nas /
NK014(pha)003:216: 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar pos bskor ba la
NK014(pha)003:217: gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs lha mo rnams kyis
NK014(pha)003:218: dur khrod rol pa'i mchod sprin rab 'byams spro ba
NK014(pha)003:219: / bden pa gnyis ldan gyi sgo dang sgo khyud
NK014(pha)003:220: kyi mtshams dang zur bzhir zla phyed rdo rjes mtshan
NK014(pha)003:221: / pa / phyi ma'i sgo logs kyi phyi zur
NK014(pha)003:222: bzhi nas zhing gi ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i
NK014(pha)003:223: rta babs snam bu brgyad pa so dang /
NK014(pha)003:226: nyi zla'i phreng ba rnams kyis spras shing bsil khang
NK014(pha)003:227: dang ldan pa'i rtser pad+ma la gnas pa'i chos kyi
NK014(pha)003:228: 'khor lo'i steng nas zhing gi gdugs phub cing /
NK014(pha)003:229: chu srin gyi phrug gu zung gis brten pa /
NK014(pha)003:230: phyi nang gi sgo thams cad la rus sbal gyi ma them /
NK014(pha)003:233: zhing gi sgo glegs rnams kyis spras pa /
NK014(pha)003:234: sgo phyi ma'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la /
NK014(pha)003:235: skyes bu gsal shing gis phug pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:236: t+aa la'i ljon pa rnams thod tshal rgyu ma la brgyus pa'i phreng bas bres shing /
NK014(pha)003:237: rak+ta'i rdzing bu rlabs phreng 'khrug pa brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK014(pha)003:238: dkyil 'khor de'i nang gi khyams phyi ma khrag mtsho dang /
NK014(pha)003:239: nang ma gser khyams su gnas pa /
NK014(pha)003:240: thod skam gyi brtsigs pa che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:241: gru chad bzhi glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa'i steng du /
NK014(pha)003:242: bde na pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:243: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa lte ba dang bcas pa
NK014(pha)003:244: rnams rim pa bzhin khyad par du gyur pas sbags
NK014(pha)003:245: pa / nang lha chen po brgyad kyi ka ba
NK014(pha)003:246: rus sbal gyi ka gdan dang ldan pas btegs pa'i
NK014(pha)003:247: steng na tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi gdung zlum dang bcas
NK014(pha)003:248: pa / pa / klu bdud kyi phyam dang /
NK014(pha)003:251: nyi zla'i mthongs dkar dang bcas pa'i dbus phyur bur
NK014(pha)003:252: lha chen po'i thod pas zlum por phub pa'i rtse
NK014(pha)003:253: mor tsit+ta'i tog gis brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)003:254: nang gi steng 'og rnams shar dkar /
NK014(pha)003:259: 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrug cing 'bar ba la sogs
NK014(pha)003:260: te dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas khang gi mtshan
NK014(pha)003:262: dngas shing sgrib pa med par kun tu gsal ba /
NK014(pha)003:263: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i lte
NK014(pha)003:264: ba la rdzogs pa'i phyi rol srung ba'i khor yug
NK014(pha)003:265: gi nang du r+au tra longs spyod dang bcas pa
NK014(pha)003:266: dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod chen po brgyad /
NK014(pha)003:268: de'i rtsa ba la gnas pa'i phyogs skyong brgyad /
NK014(pha)003:269: yal ga la brten pa'i zhing skyong brgyad /
NK014(pha)003:271: de la rol pa'i klu brgyad /
NK014(pha)003:277: mchod rten rnams kyang brgyad brgyad /
NK014(pha)003:278: thams cad du grub pa dang rig 'dzin /
NK014(pha)003:279: dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs dang /
NK014(pha)003:281: sha za 'byung po'i tshogs rnams ha har rgod cing gar rtse ba /
NK014(pha)003:282: bya dang gcan gzan gtum mo mang po lang long du rgyu zhing /
NK014(pha)003:288: 'thor ba la sogs pa'i sha rus gsar rnying sna
NK014(pha)003:289: tshogs pa gcal du bkram zhing spungs pas yongs su
NK014(pha)003:291: lnga pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:296: yon tan gyi che ba dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:297: sna tshogs pad+ma dang zla nyi brtsegs pa'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK014(pha)003:298: de rnams kyi steng du ma h+aa de wa bam /
NK014(pha)003:304: gdug can zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags su /
NK014(pha)003:305: dbus su dbang phyug dang drag po /
NK014(pha)003:309: byang du gnod sbyin rnams rang rang gi chung ma
NK014(pha)003:310: dang bcas pa khyo shug bsnol ba re re'i steng
NK014(pha)003:311: du / dug lnga gnas su dag pa'i brda //
NK014(pha)003:312: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK014(pha)003:313: gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni //
NK014(pha)003:314: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK014(pha)003:315: zhes byol song gtso bo brgyad po re res dregs pa pho mo bardzisa pa /
NK014(pha)003:316: 'khor lo'i grwa dang gru chad bzhi gser khyams kyi phyogs mtshams brgyad por /
NK014(pha)003:318: ti ra bam las nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan re re /
NK014(pha)003:319: khrag khyams kyi phyogs mtshams drug drug dang sgo bzhi'i
NK014(pha)003:320: nang du zhing gi gdan re re gsal bar bsam
NK014(pha)003:321: mo // gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gnyis /
NK014(pha)003:322: bdag nyid kyi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)003:323: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:325: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK014(pha)003:326: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK014(pha)003:327: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:328: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK014(pha)003:329: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK014(pha)003:330: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis //
NK014(pha)003:331: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad de //
NK014(pha)003:332: gnyis med 'khril bas dgyes par thim //
NK014(pha)003:333: nam mkhar gnas pa'i rgyu'i he ru ka dbus kyi
NK014(pha)003:334: gdan la bzhugs pa de nyid dpal chen po sku
NK014(pha)003:336: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin par gyur te /
NK014(pha)003:337: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon du phyung ste /
NK014(pha)003:338: he he zhes dgyes pa'i mdangs kyis yab la btud cing /
NK014(pha)003:339: pad+ma rgyas par mdzad nas gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas rol bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:340: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+da la phata phata ha la ha la h'u /
NK014(pha)003:341: zhes brjod pas yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyii sems sprin las /
NK014(pha)003:342: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas khyab par /
NK014(pha)003:343: khro bo 'chol ba mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi char 'bebs pa dpag tu med pa spros /
NK014(pha)003:344: ltas chen po bco lngas gdug pa can kyi tshogs thams cad tshar gcad par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:345: mkha' khyab kyi khro bo'i sprin rnams slar 'dus pa las /
NK014(pha)003:346: rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo rnams rang la thim pas 'bras bu'i he ru kar gyur pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:347: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:348: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:349: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po //
NK014(pha)003:350: dgyes mdzad badz+ra he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:351: mthing nag char sprin lta bur gnag /
NK014(pha)003:352: nyi ma bye ba'i gzi byin can //
NK014(pha)003:353: dbu gsum g.yas dkar g.yon dmar mthing //
NK014(pha)003:354: khros pa'i nyams can dmar zlum spyan /
NK014(pha)003:355: gsum gsum rnam par 'gyur ba'i zhal //
NK014(pha)003:356: mche gtsigs ljags ni glog ltar 'khyug /
NK014(pha)003:357: rdo rje'i gad mos srid gsum g.yo //
NK014(pha)003:358: shangs nas mi bzad h'u sgra 'byin //
NK014(pha)003:359: rdzi smin sma ra me ltar 'bar //
NK014(pha)003:360: gtum rngams zhal ni khro gnyer bsdus //
NK014(pha)003:361: sku che yan lag rags pa la //
NK014(pha)003:362: rdo rje'i ba spus kun nas bltams //
NK014(pha)003:363: sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa //
NK014(pha)003:364: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs su rung //
NK014(pha)003:365: gar gyi nyams dgus rab tu rgyas //
NK014(pha)003:366: phyag drug g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis //
NK014(pha)003:368: gnyis pa rtse lnga b+han+d+ha dmar //
NK014(pha)003:369: gsum pas zhing dbyug stong khams 'degs //
NK014(pha)003:370: zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang g.yon pa bskum //
NK014(pha)003:371: gyad kyi dor stabs chen pos rol //
NK014(pha)003:372: thod skam rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan sogs //
NK014(pha)003:373: dur khrod dpal gyi chas rnams rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:374: snyan gong nyi zla'i 'od zer spro //
NK014(pha)003:375: yum chen kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK014(pha)003:376: sngo skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NK014(pha)003:377: spyan gsum lang tshos sgeg pa'i nyams //
NK014(pha)003:378: phyag g.yas dril bus yab la 'khyud //
NK014(pha)003:379: g.yon pa dung khrag gtso la stob //
NK014(pha)003:380: gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs sogs //
NK014(pha)003:381: dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan //
NK014(pha)003:382: g.yon brkyang g.yas bskum gtso dang 'khril //
NK014(pha)003:383: bskal pa'i me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NK014(pha)003:384: de bzhin gshegs dang rin po che //
NK014(pha)003:385: pad+ma las kyi rigs la sogs //
NK014(pha)003:386: thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid can //
NK014(pha)003:387: rigs bzhi'i he ru kar gyur nas //
NK014(pha)003:388: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK014(pha)003:389: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:390: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:391: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:392: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:393: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:394: pad+ma kri d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:395: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:396: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:397: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK014(pha)003:398: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK014(pha)003:399: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bgrad //
NK014(pha)003:400: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK014(pha)003:401: rngams pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrog /
NK014(pha)003:402: sbrul dang thod phreng nyi zla'i chas //
NK014(pha)003:404: rdo rje dung chen gang ba dang //
NK014(pha)003:405: ral gri dgra s+t+wa gshol la sogs //
NK014(pha)003:406: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs te //
NK014(pha)003:408: rjes su chags pas snyoms par zhugs //
NK014(pha)003:409: he zhes dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra las //
NK014(pha)003:410: sbyor mtshams byang chub sems kyi sprin //
NK014(pha)003:411: khro mo brgyad kyi rnam par thon //
NK014(pha)003:412: goo r+ai ma dang tsoo r+ai ma //
NK014(pha)003:413: pra mo ha dang be ta l+ai //
NK014(pha)003:415: sma sha ni dang tsan+da li //
NK014(pha)003:416: rtsibs mchan dang ni grwa bzhir 'khod //
NK014(pha)003:417: he zhes dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra las //
NK014(pha)003:418: phra men chen mo brgyad thon te //
NK014(pha)003:419: seng ge stag dang wa spyang gdong //
NK014(pha)003:420: bzhad gdong kang+ka bya rog gdong //
NK014(pha)003:421: 'ug gdong brgyad po gser khyams kyi //
NK014(pha)003:422: phyogs mtshams la ni rim bzhin 'khod //
NK014(pha)003:423: slar yang dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra ni //
NK014(pha)003:424: he zhes brjod pas byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)003:425: sgo skyong bzhi yi rnam par thon //
NK014(pha)003:426: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK014(pha)003:427: rta gdong ma dang phag gdong ma //
NK014(pha)003:428: seng gdong ma dang spyang gdong ma //
NK014(pha)003:429: kun kyang shin tu khros pa'i nyams //
NK014(pha)003:430: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK014(pha)003:431: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgyas rab mdzes shing //
NK014(pha)003:432: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:433: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK014(pha)003:434: rang gi stan dang lag cha dang //
NK014(pha)003:435: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK014(pha)003:436: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK014(pha)003:437: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK014(pha)003:439: gnyis pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba la gnyis /
NK014(pha)003:443: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:444: ye shes zer gyis lus rtog sbyangs //
NK014(pha)003:445: gser zhun lta bu'i sems dag las //
NK014(pha)003:447: thugs kar thiim nas sku yi dbyibs //
NK014(pha)003:448: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkhar //
NK014(pha)003:449: chos sku byang chub sems su gnas //
NK014(pha)003:450: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK014(pha)003:451: h'u ha ha phata ces byung nas //
NK014(pha)003:452: byang chub sems su gcig par thim //
NK014(pha)003:453: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas kun tu bzang po byang
NK014(pha)003:454: chub sems kyi bdag nyid rnam smin gyi lus kyi
NK014(pha)003:456: dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor 'dud pa'i rnam pas 'khor par bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)003:457: hoh sems nyid theg par rab nges pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:458: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:459: sangs rgyas rdo rje he ru ka'i //
NK014(pha)003:460: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas kyis //
NK014(pha)003:461: sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyor cig /
NK014(pha)003:462: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ho /
NK014(pha)003:463: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:464: zhes bskul bas lha rnams kyis rjes su gnang ste /
NK014(pha)003:465: thabs dang shes rab kyi 'od zer bdag la 'phros
NK014(pha)003:466: pas sems kyi rtog pa dang de las gyur pa'i
NK014(pha)003:467: lus ngag sbyangs nas gnyis su med pa' ye shes
NK014(pha)003:468: gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i rang bzhin gser zhun lta
NK014(pha)003:469: bu'i 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa la /
NK014(pha)003:470: lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer 'bru gsum gyi rnam par 'phros te thim pas /
NK014(pha)003:471: de nyid +aahmh'u gsum du gyur nas rim bzhin h'u
NK014(pha)003:472: la zhugs pa zla ba dang rlung dkyil la gnas
NK014(pha)003:473: par gyur / de rlung gis bteg pas bung ba
NK014(pha)003:474: me tog la lding ba ltar lha tshogs rnams la
NK014(pha)003:475: lan gsum bskor nas gtso bo'i thugs kar thim /
NK014(pha)003:476: yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i dga' ba'i rol mos
NK014(pha)003:477: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba sku'i dbyibs brgyud
NK014(pha)003:478: / rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+mara son pa 'od kyi gong bur gnas pa las /
NK014(pha)003:479: gtso bo yab yum kyang rjes su chags pa'i sbyor bas bde ba'i ngo bor zhu bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:480: de nas h'u ha he phata ces brjod pas /
NK014(pha)003:483: sgo ma bzhi rnams rim bzhin dbus kyi thig le
NK014(pha)003:484: la ro gcig tu gyur pa las gser zhun lta
NK014(pha)003:485: bu'i 'od kyi gong bur 'bar bar gyur /
NK014(pha)003:486: gnyis pa chad mtha' bsal ba la gsum /
NK014(pha)003:487: gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:488: de la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK014(pha)003:490: dang po gtso bo bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:492: gdan steng gi 'od phung de nyid h'u zung gcig tu gyur /
NK014(pha)003:494: de las 'od zer mkha' khyab tu 'phros /
NK014(pha)003:500: rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu h'u yig gis mtshan par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:503: sngar bzhin 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK014(pha)003:504: badz+r+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:505: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:506: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he ru
NK014(pha)003:507: ka sku mdog mthing nag char sprin ltar gnag cing
NK014(pha)003:508: nyi ma bye ba'i gzi byin 'bar ba /
NK014(pha)003:509: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:510: dbu gsum gyi g.yas zhal dkar la bzhad pa /
NK014(pha)003:511: g.yon zhal dmar la gshe ba /
NK014(pha)003:512: dbus zhal mthing nag drag por khros pa'i nyams can /
NK014(pha)003:513: zhal re re la dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum
NK014(pha)003:514: gsum dang ldan pa rnam par 'gyur ba'i zhal gdangs
NK014(pha)003:517: rdo rje'i gad mos sa gsum g.yo ba /
NK014(pha)003:518: khro gnyer bsdus pa'i shangs nas mi bzad pa'i h'u sgra 'byin pa /
NK014(pha)003:519: rdzi smin sma ra las 'bar ba'i me 'khyog por spro ba /
NK014(pha)003:520: sku che zhing yan lag rags pa /
NK014(pha)003:521: lang tsho rgyas pa'i 'gyur bag can /
NK014(pha)003:522: rdo rje'i ba spus gtams pa /
NK014(pha)003:523: sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa /
NK014(pha)003:524: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs su rung /
NK014(pha)003:525: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba ste /
NK014(pha)003:526: gar gyi nyams dgus rab tu rgyas pa /
NK014(pha)003:527: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:528: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse
NK014(pha)003:529: dgu dang dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa
NK014(pha)003:530: / gnyis pas rdo rje rtse lnga dang /
NK014(pha)003:531: b+hany+dza dmar gyis gang ba thogs pa /
NK014(pha)003:532: gsum pas zhing gi dbyug pa dang stong gi 'jig rten 'degs pa /
NK014(pha)003:533: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK014(pha)003:535: g.yon bskums pa'i gyad chen po'i stabs kyis stan la rol ba /
NK014(pha)003:536: dbu re re la thod pa skam po lnga lnga rigs lnga'i cod pan gyis dbu brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)003:537: 'dzag pa'i mgo bo lnga bcu'i do shal dang /
NK014(pha)003:538: thod pa tshal bu'i dpung rgyan can /
NK014(pha)003:539: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK014(pha)003:540: glang po che'i ko ba rlon pas stod g.yogs shing /
NK014(pha)003:541: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs grol ba /
NK014(pha)003:542: klu rgyal rigs dkar pos skra chings /
NK014(pha)003:543: rje'u rigs ser pos snyan cha /
NK014(pha)003:544: bram ze'i rigs dmar pos se mo do dang mgur chu /
NK014(pha)003:545: dmangs rigs ljang gus ska rags dang do shal /
NK014(pha)003:546: gdol pa nag pos phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste /
NK014(pha)003:547: thams cad kyang gdug pa'i sbrul gyi rnam pa can /
NK014(pha)003:548: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK014(pha)003:549: smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK014(pha)003:550: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris kyis mtshan pa ste dur khrod rol pa'i chas brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)003:551: dpal gyi chas bcu sku la rdzogs shing /
NK014(pha)003:552: snyan gong nas nyi ma'i 'od zer spro pa /
NK014(pha)003:553: yum kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma sngo skya zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum /
NK014(pha)003:554: gcer bu skra grol zhing lang tshos sgeg pa'i nyams 'gyur can /
NK014(pha)003:555: g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK014(pha)003:556: g.yon thod pa khrag gis bkang ba gtso bo'i zhal du stob pa /
NK014(pha)003:557: gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs sogs dur khrod rol pa'i chas can zhabs g.yon brkyangs shing /
NK014(pha)003:558: g.yas bskums pas gtso bo dang dgyes par 'khril ba /
NK014(pha)003:559: stong pa nyid dang snying rje chen po zung du 'jug pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK014(pha)003:560: bskal pa'i me'i phung po rab tu 'bar ba'i klong
NK014(pha)003:561: na khams gsum pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i ngo bor
NK014(pha)003:562: bzhugs pa'o // gnyis la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:563: rang gi thugs rin po che'i gur khyim lta bu'i
NK014(pha)003:564: nang du nyi ma la gnas pa'i rang 'dra'i ye
NK014(pha)003:565: shes sems dpa' / de'i thugs kar ting 'dzin sems
NK014(pha)003:566: dpa' rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i lte bar h'u yig
NK014(pha)003:567: phra mo 'bar bas mtshan par bsams la /
NK014(pha)003:568: de las 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK014(pha)003:569: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dbang gi lha rigs
NK014(pha)003:570: lnga yab yum gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs
NK014(pha)003:572: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)003:574: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK014(pha)003:575: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK014(pha)003:576: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bar
NK014(pha)003:577: bsam zhing / rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'jog cing dbang sngags rnams brjod pa ste /
NK014(pha)003:578: rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK014(pha)003:579: ma h+aa shunya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)003:580: phyag rgya de nyid las mdzub mo gnyis brkyang pa dpral bar 'jog cing /
NK014(pha)003:581: ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na /
NK014(pha)003:582: srin lag gnyis brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas par 'jog cing /
NK014(pha)003:583: ma h+aa sa ma ta dz+ny+aa na /
NK014(pha)003:584: mthe bong gnyis brkyang pa ltag par 'jog cing /
NK014(pha)003:585: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na /
NK014(pha)003:586: mathe'u chung gnyis brkyang ba rna ltag g.yon par 'jog cing /
NK014(pha)003:587: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na /
NK014(pha)003:588: zhes rim par dbang bskur bas /
NK014(pha)003:589: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK014(pha)003:590: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur bas kun brtags la gzhan dbang gis rgyas btab /
NK014(pha)003:591: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa las gzhan dbang
NK014(pha)003:592: la yongs grub kyi rgyas btab pas ye shes 'gyur
NK014(pha)003:593: ba med pa'i brdar dbu gtsug na rdo rje phyed
NK014(pha)003:594: pa dang / rigs bdag rdo rje mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:595: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK014(pha)003:596: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK014(pha)003:597: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK014(pha)003:598: la thim de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:599: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor
NK014(pha)003:600: lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur par bsam zhing
NK014(pha)003:601: / rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs la /
NK014(pha)003:602: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)003:603: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po de'i
NK014(pha)003:604: 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK014(pha)003:605: thugs rgyud bskul / gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK014(pha)003:607: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:608: +aam yongs su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:609: rdo rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par bzhag /
NK014(pha)003:610: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)003:611: snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'u sngon po /
NK014(pha)003:612: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK014(pha)003:613: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK014(pha)003:615: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs da nga gnyis su med par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:616: h'u yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:617: rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar bzhag /
NK014(pha)003:618: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a h+aam /
NK014(pha)003:620: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du gsal lo //
NK014(pha)003:621: gsum pa sras kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la /
NK014(pha)003:622: rigs bzhi'i he ru ka bskyed pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:626: lha tshogs spro ba gnyis las dang po ni /
NK014(pha)003:627: yab kyi gsang gnas h'u las ye shes kyi rdo
NK014(pha)003:628: rje rtse mo lnga pa'i lte bar byang chub kyi
NK014(pha)003:629: sems dkar por gnas pa'i bu ga phata kyis bkag
NK014(pha)003:630: pa / yum gyi mkha' pam las pad+ma 'dab ma
NK014(pha)003:631: brgyad pa'i lte bar nyi ma la rak+ta +aam dmar
NK014(pha)003:632: por gnas pa'i ge sar es mtshan par mos la
NK014(pha)003:636: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK014(pha)003:637: sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te /
NK014(pha)003:638: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis 'khyud sdom sprad nas /
NK014(pha)003:639: h'u h'u h'u zhes gnyis su med par snyoms par
NK014(pha)003:640: zhugs pas bde ba chen po'i sgra dang 'od zer
NK014(pha)003:641: gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bkug nas zhal
NK014(pha)003:642: du zhugs / rjes su chags pa'i mes byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba /
NK014(pha)003:644: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+mora lan gsum du
NK014(pha)003:645: spros pa las lha rnams kyi sa bon yig 'bru'i
NK014(pha)003:646: dkyil 'khor bkra lam gyis gsal bar gyur bar bsam
NK014(pha)003:647: mo // gnyis pa lha tshogs spro ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:648: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)003:649: sarba du sh+tan+da ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK014(pha)003:651: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:653: dbus kyi h'u gnyis badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi skur gyur /
NK014(pha)003:654: phata dzah zhes pas mkha' las spros nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs par gyur s+pha ra na phata /
NK014(pha)003:656: de las 'od zer spro ba dang bsdu ba'i sbyor bas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te /
NK014(pha)003:657: bdag nyid gtso bo yab yum la gnyis su med par gyur /
NK014(pha)003:658: de bzhin du sa bon yig 'bru'i dkyil 'khor gzhan rnams kyang lha skur rdzogs pa /
NK014(pha)003:659: phata dzah zhes mkha' las spros te rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:660: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK014(pha)003:661: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan+ta ka ha na
NK014(pha)003:662: da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:663: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dush+tam h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:664: shar gyi rtsibs la bud+d+ha he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal smug nag /
NK014(pha)003:665: g.yas dkar g.yon ser ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)003:666: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)003:667: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)003:668: tha mas zhing dbyug dang tri shul 'dzin pa yum
NK014(pha)003:669: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma smug nag dang mnyam
NK014(pha)003:670: par sbyor ba / rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK014(pha)003:671: ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan+ta ka ha na
NK014(pha)003:672: da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:673: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai bi dam h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:674: lho'i rtsibs la rat+na he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal ser nag /
NK014(pha)003:675: g.yas sdo g.yon dmar ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)003:676: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rin po che dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)003:677: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)003:678: tha mas zhing dbyug dang dgra s+t+wa 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:679: yum rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma ser mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)003:680: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK014(pha)003:681: sarba du sh+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK014(pha)003:683: h+r+ai sh+au ta sa ma ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:684: nub kyi rtsibs la pad+ma he ru la sku dang rtsa zhal dmar nag /
NK014(pha)003:685: g.yas dkar g.yon ser ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)003:686: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:687: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)003:688: tha mas zhing dbyug dang rnge'u chung 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:689: yum pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma dmar mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)003:690: karma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba
NK014(pha)003:691: du sh+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK014(pha)003:692: h'u h'u phata / sarba a mo g+ha ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai bi shwa h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:693: byang gi rtsibs la karma he ru ka sku dang rtsa zhal ljang nag /
NK014(pha)003:694: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba'i zhal gsum /
NK014(pha)003:695: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK014(pha)003:696: gnyis pas rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK014(pha)003:697: tha mas zhing dbyug dang thong gshol 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:698: yum karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma ljang mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK014(pha)003:699: khrag 'thung yab yum thams cad kyang gar dgu'i ros sgeg cing /
NK014(pha)003:700: rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo dang mthun pa /
NK014(pha)003:701: rang rang gi gdan la g.yas brkyang pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:702: phata dzah zhes brjod pas 'khor lo'i grwa dang gru chad bzhi la /
NK014(pha)003:704: rtsibs mchan gyi shar lhor goo r+ai ma sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:706: lho nub tu tsoo ri ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK014(pha)003:708: nub byang du pra mo ha dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)003:710: byang shar du be ta l+ai nag mo g.yas rdo rje 'phyar zhing g.yon byis pa'i bam za ba /
NK014(pha)003:712: gru chad kyi shar lhor puk+ka swi dmar ser zhing chung gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK014(pha)003:714: lho nub tu g+hasma ljang gu g.yas pa'i rdo rjes g.yon gyi dung dmar dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK014(pha)003:716: nub byang du sma sha mthing nag byis pa'i ro bzung nas snying za ba /
NK014(pha)003:718: byang shar du tsan+da li ser skya mchog lus 'bral
NK014(pha)003:719: ba thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum
NK014(pha)003:721: skra ser po gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK014(pha)003:722: gcer bu dur khrod rol pa'i chas can g.yon brkyang pa'i stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:723: phata dzah zhes spros pas gser khyams kyi phyogs mtshams brgyad du /
NK014(pha)003:725: shar du seng gdong ser mo phyag gnyis thugs kar
NK014(pha)003:726: gyen du bsnol bas ti ra bzung nas za ba
NK014(pha)003:727: / badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK014(pha)003:728: lhor stag gdong ma dmar mo phyag gnyis mthur du bsnol nas ro bzung ba /
NK014(pha)003:729: badz+ra sh+ri g+aa la mu kha he /
NK014(pha)003:730: nub tu wa gdong ma nag mo zhing chung bzung nas lces bldag pa /
NK014(pha)003:731: badz+ra shwa n+aa mu kha he /
NK014(pha)003:732: byang du spyang gdong ma mthing ga zhing chung gi
NK014(pha)003:733: khog pa 'bral ba ste mche ba can bzhi dang
NK014(pha)003:735: shar lhor bzhad gdong ma dmar ser g.yon zhing chung
NK014(pha)003:736: bzung ba'i rgyu ma g.yas pas drangs nas gsol ba
NK014(pha)003:738: lho nub tu kang+ka'i mgo can dmar skya bam ro'i rkang lag bzung nas phrag par 'gel pa /
NK014(pha)003:739: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK014(pha)003:740: nub byang du bya rog gdong ma nag mo g.yas ral gri g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:741: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he /
NK014(pha)003:742: byang shar du 'ug gdong ma mthing ga g.yas lcags kyu dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa ste /
NK014(pha)003:744: thams cad gcer bu rang rang khros pa'i zhal can
NK014(pha)003:745: drag mo'i rnam 'gyur dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang
NK014(pha)003:746: ldan pa'o // phata dzah zhes spros pas sgo bzhi'i nang du /
NK014(pha)003:747: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK014(pha)003:748: shar sgor rta gdong ma sngon po lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:750: lho sgor phag gdong ma nag mo mche zhag 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:752: nub sgor seng gdong ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:753: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu ho /
NK014(pha)003:754: byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:755: bzhi ka'ang gcer bu gtum zhing khros pa'i nyams can
NK014(pha)003:756: dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan te zhal phyir phyogs
NK014(pha)003:757: nas 'khod pa'o // gnyis pa 'khor khyams dbang phyug ma bskyed pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:758: bdag nyid badz+ra he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK014(pha)003:759: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /

NK014(pha)003:762: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /

NK014(pha)003:774: shar stod nas g.yas skor du rim pa bzhin /

NK014(pha)003:776: tshangs ma dmar ser pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK014(pha)003:777: lha chen mo dkar ljang tri shul 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:778: rtogs 'dod ma sngon mo 'khor lo 'chang ba /
NK014(pha)003:779: gzhon nu ma dmar mo mdung thung 'phen pa /
NK014(pha)003:780: brgya byin dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:787: lho stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK014(pha)003:788: rdo rje ma ser mo dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK014(pha)003:789: bdud rtsi ma dmar mo pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK014(pha)003:790: zla ba ma dkar mo pun+da ri ka 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:791: be con ma ljang nag dbyug tho 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)003:792: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK014(pha)003:793: za ba ma ljang nag rgyu ma 'dren pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:795: ru ti ra ma t+ya b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)003:796: e ka tsa ri ni b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)003:800: nub stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK014(pha)003:801: dga' ba dmar mo ka tar 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)003:802: stobs chen mo gshol mda' 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:803: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod pa /
NK014(pha)003:804: 'dod pa dmar mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK014(pha)003:805: nor srung ma dkar mo bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:806: rlung lha ma sngon mo ba dan 'phyar ba'o //
NK014(pha)003:807: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)003:813: byang stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK014(pha)003:814: gsod byed ma dkar mo ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:815: mi mo dmar mo gsal shing 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)003:816: phag mo nag mo mche zhags 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:817: rgan byed ma dmar mo zhing chung za ba /
NK014(pha)003:818: sna chen ma dkar ljang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK014(pha)003:819: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags 'dzin pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:820: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)003:824: shar sgor rdo rje nag mo chen mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:825: lho sgor rdo rjer mo ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:826: nub sgor rdo rje bum sna ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)003:827: byang sgor rdo rje gsus 'dzin ma ljang nag dril bu 'khrol ba ste /
NK014(pha)003:828: thams cad kyang gtum zhing 'khros pa drag mo'i nyams can dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan te /
NK014(pha)003:829: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i rnam rol cir yang 'char ba
NK014(pha)003:830: me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na gnas pa'i lha thams
NK014(pha)003:831: cad kyi srog gi go ra ye shes sems dpa'
NK014(pha)003:832: dngas ma'i srog yig dang bcas pas mtshan pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:833: h'u ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes brjod pas dkyil
NK014(pha)003:834: 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams cad gsal brtan sgrib pa
NK014(pha)003:835: med pa 'bar ba'i 'od zer mkha' khyab tu 'phro
NK014(pha)003:836: ba'i bdag nyid du gnas par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:837: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la drug ste /
NK014(pha)003:844: dang po la'ang nang gses bzhi'i dang po snyam gsan dbab pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:845: gtso bo'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar dngas mi'i
NK014(pha)003:846: thugs srog h'u mthing ga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK014(pha)003:848: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bskul bas /
NK014(pha)003:849: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las /
NK014(pha)003:850: gzugs sku lnga bcu rtsa brgyad sgyu 'phrul ye shes
NK014(pha)003:851: kyi 'khor lo'i rnam pa can du sad par bsams
NK014(pha)003:853: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK014(pha)003:854: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK014(pha)003:855: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK014(pha)003:856: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK014(pha)003:857: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK014(pha)003:858: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yis //
NK014(pha)003:859: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:860: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)003:862: gnyis pa spyan drang ba dngos ni /
NK014(pha)003:864: rdo rje snying po srid gsum mgon //
NK014(pha)003:865: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal dang ldan //
NK014(pha)003:867: rdo rje khrag 'thung gshegs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:869: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang longs spyod cing //
NK014(pha)003:870: gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK014(pha)003:871: tshogs kyi slob dpon gshegs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:872: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pa //
NK014(pha)003:873: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:874: ye shes rtog pa'i khyad par las //
NK014(pha)003:875: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs dang gshegs //
NK014(pha)003:876: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)003:877: e h+ye hi a na ya dzahmh'u bam hoh dam
NK014(pha)003:878: tshig pa'i thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu zhags
NK014(pha)003:879: pa lcags sgrog dril bu'i rnam pa can du 'phros
NK014(pha)003:880: / ye shes kyi 'khor lo bkug bcings bsdams la dgyes pa bskyed nas /
NK014(pha)003:881: ram zhes pas dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dabs 'byar du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:882: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:883: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya /
NK014(pha)003:884: +aahbadz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya +aah h'u badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h'u /
NK014(pha)003:885: s+w+aa badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK014(pha)003:886: h+aa badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aa /
NK014(pha)003:887: zhes brjod pas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang ting
NK014(pha)003:888: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi sku gsung thugs
NK014(pha)003:889: yon tan phrin las rnams rang bzhin dbyer med du
NK014(pha)003:890: rtogs par bya'o // bzhi pa dngos grub bskul ba ni //
NK014(pha)003:891: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK014(pha)003:892: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:893: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK014(pha)003:894: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK014(pha)003:895: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:896: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK014(pha)003:897: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ho /
NK014(pha)003:898: zhes pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la dbyer med du bstim nas /
NK014(pha)003:899: dam tshig bskul zhing rang dbang du byas pa /
NK014(pha)003:900: lha rnams rjes chags kyi dgyes pa bskyed nas drin lan gyi tshul du /
NK014(pha)003:901: a li u li t+aa li t+aa pa i dam
NK014(pha)003:902: sh+ta go n+aa roo tri kha ram yo gi n+ai
NK014(pha)003:903: kh+aa hi he / zhes mchod la h'u ha he phata /
NK014(pha)003:904: ces brjod pas gsal zhing brtan par byas la /
NK014(pha)003:907: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK014(pha)003:908: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:909: gnyis med don gyi dngos grub mchog gi gnas //
NK014(pha)003:910: bdag la gsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:911: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u k+aa ya w+aak+ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK014(pha)003:912: gnyis pa mchod pa la phyag dang mchod pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)003:913: de gnyis gang gi tshe yang /
NK014(pha)003:914: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo las sprul pa'i
NK014(pha)003:915: he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dkyil 'khor
NK014(pha)003:916: gyi shar sgor 'khod pas sems can thams cad dang
NK014(pha)003:917: bya byed thun mong du gyur pas de dang de'i
NK014(pha)003:918: bya ba la 'jug par mos nas /
NK014(pha)003:921: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK014(pha)003:922: byams dang snying rjer dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK014(pha)003:923: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK014(pha)003:924: 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)003:925: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer gnas shing //
NK014(pha)003:926: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK014(pha)003:927: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin spro ma //
NK014(pha)003:928: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)003:929: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK014(pha)003:930: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK014(pha)003:931: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK014(pha)003:932: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)003:935: gnyis pa mchod pa la bcu gsum las /
NK014(pha)003:936: dang po phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:945: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)003:946: dril bu dung dmar 'jig rten g.yon //
NK014(pha)003:948: dpal chen ye shes thabs g.yon dkrol /

NK014(pha)003:956: kro d+hi shwa r+ai dbyings kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:957: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
