NK014(pha)003:966: dpal chen bud+d+ha thabs kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:967: rat+na he ru'i phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:968: g.yas sngon g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK014(pha)003:969: rin chen rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)003:970: dril bu dung dmar dgra s+t+wa g.yon //
NK014(pha)003:971: dpal chen rat+na thabs kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:972: pad+ma he ru'i phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:973: g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus dmar zhal //
NK014(pha)003:974: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)003:975: dril bu dung dmar rnge'u chung g.yon //
NK014(pha)003:976: dpal chen pad+ma thabs kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:977: karma he ru phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:978: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK014(pha)003:979: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK014(pha)003:980: dril bu dung dmar thong gshol g.yon //
NK014(pha)003:981: dpal chen karma thabs kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:982: rigs bzhi'i yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:983: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rigs kyi mdog /
NK014(pha)003:984: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la brten //
NK014(pha)003:985: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK014(pha)003:986: kro d+hi rigs bzhi dbyings kyi rgya //
NK014(pha)003:987: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzheng sa nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:988: mchod bzhes dam bskang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:989: gnas ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:990: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK014(pha)003:991: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK014(pha)003:992: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK014(pha)003:993: be ta byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK014(pha)003:996: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK014(pha)003:998: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1003: seng+ha kha ro bsnol seng ser //
NK014(pha)003:1004: b+y+aa g+h+r+ai gnas lhag bsnol phyir /
NK014(pha)003:1006: sri la nag mo byis bldag wa //
NK014(pha)003:1007: shwa na 'dral lta mthing ga spyang //
NK014(pha)003:1008: gri d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK014(pha)003:1009: kang+ka zhing phrag snar mgo ring //
NK014(pha)003:1010: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK014(pha)003:1011: u lu lcags kyu g.yas mdzub bkug /
NK014(pha)003:1013: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1014: mchod bzhes dam bskang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1015: sgo ma bzhi yi phyag rgya ni //
NK014(pha)003:1016: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu rang phyag 'dzin //
NK014(pha)003:1017: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK014(pha)003:1018: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK014(pha)003:1019: spyang gdong ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK014(pha)003:1020: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1021: mchod bzhes dam bskang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1028: srin mo smug nag thod srin lag mig 'bras bya /
NK014(pha)003:1030: tshangs ma dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK014(pha)003:1031: lha chen dkar ljang tri sh+au la //
NK014(pha)003:1033: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK014(pha)003:1036: rdo rje ser mo tsan dan 'thung //
NK014(pha)003:1037: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK014(pha)003:1038: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK014(pha)003:1039: bee con ljang nag dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK014(pha)003:1040: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK014(pha)003:1041: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK014(pha)003:1044: stobs chen dkar mo gshol g.yon sdigs mdzub dang g.yas rdo rje khu tshur /
NK014(pha)003:1046: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK014(pha)003:1048: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK014(pha)003:1049: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK014(pha)003:1050: gsod byed dkar mo ral gri 'dzin //
NK014(pha)003:1051: mi mo dmar mo gsal shing 'phyar //
NK014(pha)003:1052: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK014(pha)003:1053: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK014(pha)003:1054: sna chen dkar ljang thod khrag 'thung //
NK014(pha)003:1055: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags can //
NK014(pha)003:1056: rdo rje nag mo lcags sgo ma bzhi'i rang phyag /
NK014(pha)003:1058: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK014(pha)003:1059: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog sdoms //
NK014(pha)003:1060: rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK014(pha)003:1061: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1062: mchod bzhes dam bskang dngos grub rtsol //
NK014(pha)003:1063: zhes rim pa bzhin lha so so'i phyag rgya mdun du bca' zhing bsgyur ba'i mthar /
NK014(pha)003:1064: khu tshur kha sbyar barla g.yon steng du 'jog /
NK014(pha)003:1065: yum rgya g.yas dang yab rgya g.yon du 'grol lo //
NK014(pha)003:1066: phyag rgya bzhi'i mtshan nyid ni zhi bar bshad pa bzhin 'dir yang nges par bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:1069: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK014(pha)003:1070: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK014(pha)003:1071: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK014(pha)003:1072: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK014(pha)003:1073: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK014(pha)003:1074: kheb+h+yah sarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK014(pha)003:1075: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)003:1076: zhes phyi nang gsang ba'i 'dod yon gyi dngos po
NK014(pha)003:1077: mtha' dag spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu
NK014(pha)003:1078: bzang po'i mchod sprin chen por 'bul lo //
NK014(pha)003:1080: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1081: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK014(pha)003:1082: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil nas kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1083: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1084: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK014(pha)003:1085: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha ni ga ga
NK014(pha)003:1086: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)003:1087: zhes rim par phyag zhabs bsil zhing zhal du gsol bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)003:1089: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK014(pha)003:1091: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK014(pha)003:1093: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK014(pha)003:1094: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i mchod pa rol //
NK014(pha)003:1095: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK014(pha)003:1097: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi tu /
NK014(pha)003:1099: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK014(pha)003:1100: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK014(pha)003:1103: snying rje thabs dang shes rab las //
NK014(pha)003:1105: pa na pem pe nu sogs kyi mthar /
NK014(pha)003:1106: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu //
NK014(pha)003:1107: dbang gi phyag na sgron ma bsnams //
NK014(pha)003:1109: dga' ba thabs dang shes rab las //
NK014(pha)003:1110: badz+ra lo ke'i mchod par rol //
NK014(pha)003:1112: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+ai //
NK014(pha)003:1113: tsan dan bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK014(pha)003:1115: btang snyoms thabs dang shes rab las //
NK014(pha)003:1118: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga g+han+d+he gan /
NK014(pha)003:1119: lha mo rnams kyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs mchod
NK014(pha)003:1120: nas shangs la sogs pa'i dbang po so so la
NK014(pha)003:1123: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)003:1124: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1125: mchod chen thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1127: skyes dang skyes lan gyi tshul du lha rnams mnyes /
NK014(pha)003:1128: lha mo rnams slar byung ste rang gi gnas bzhir
NK014(pha)003:1129: thim pas sku gsung thugs phrin las bzhi'i dngos grub
NK014(pha)003:1133: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK014(pha)003:1134: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK014(pha)003:1135: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK014(pha)003:1136: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK014(pha)003:1137: rgyud lnga sems can kun bsgral phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1138: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK014(pha)003:1139: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK014(pha)003:1140: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyis //
NK014(pha)003:1141: thugs dam dbyings nas bskang ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1142: 'di ni sngon gyi tha tshig ste //
NK014(pha)003:1143: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid du //
NK014(pha)003:1144: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK014(pha)003:1145: bla med 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1146: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa i mra ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1147: zhes spyir dbul zhing bye brag tu dkon mchog 'grel las /
NK014(pha)003:1148: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)003:1149: de stsol bla ma de rgya lhag pa'i lha //
NK014(pha)003:1150: de dbang sprul pa'i 'khor lor bcas pa la //
NK014(pha)003:1151: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1152: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1154: kun bzang rigs lnga rigs gsum dra ma lnga //
NK014(pha)003:1155: lung bstan rdo rje u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK014(pha)003:1156: drang srong b+ha shi pra b+ha hasti la //
NK014(pha)003:1157: sman mchod sarba rgyal dbang pad+ma k+aa ra gnyags lo dang //
NK014(pha)003:1158: sog po lha dpal gnubs chen sras slob brgyud //
NK014(pha)003:1159: shes rab mchog dang ye shes 'byung gnas la //
NK014(pha)003:1160: sman sarba grub thob zur chen zur chung ka chen bzhi //
NK014(pha)003:1161: gsang bdag sgro phug pan chen rong pa'i zhabs //
NK014(pha)003:1163: sman mchod sarba pur+n+yee d+h+aa dza chos seng bud+d+ha sh+r+ai //
NK014(pha)003:1164: bsod nams mgon po sgrol chen dge 'dun 'bum //
NK014(pha)003:1165: sh+aakya bshes gnyen bra bo chos 'bum la //
NK014(pha)003:1166: sman mchod sarba rat+na b+ha dra rdo rje dpal bzang po //
NK014(pha)003:1167: dan 'bag gzhon nu kun mkhyen dri med 'od //
NK014(pha)003:1168: gtad rgya lung rdzogs 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK014(pha)003:1169: sman mchod sarba mngon rdzogs rgyal po khrag 'thung yab yum bcu //
NK014(pha)003:1170: goo r+ai phra men gdong mo dbang phyug sogs //
NK014(pha)003:1171: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK014(pha)003:1172: sman mchod sarba mdor na rab 'byams dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK014(pha)003:1173: gnas yul d+aak+ki dam can chos skyong dang //
NK014(pha)003:1174: zhing skyong gzhi bdag dkar phyogs skyong ba'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1175: dus gsum pha ma 'gro ba rigs drug la //
NK014(pha)003:1176: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1177: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1178: zhes gu h+ya lag gi phyag rgyas gtor bas ye
NK014(pha)003:1179: shes kyi bdud rtsi'i zegs ma mkha' la sprin bzhin
NK014(pha)003:1180: du chags pa las bdud rtsi'i char chen po babs
NK014(pha)003:1181: te lha tshogs thams cad mnyes shing tshims par bsams
NK014(pha)003:1182: la mthar dngos grub blang ba ni rang gi lce
NK014(pha)003:1184: sman gyi steng du +aahmh'u gsum bsgoms te /
NK014(pha)003:1185: +aahmh'u rdo rje lce yi dam tshig la //
NK014(pha)003:1186: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum sgom //
NK014(pha)003:1187: bdun rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman /
NK014(pha)003:1188: myangs na dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK014(pha)003:1189: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kwa ya sid+d+hi /
NK014(pha)003:1191: zhes rim par brjod cing blangs nas lce la bzhag
NK014(pha)003:1192: pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam
NK014(pha)003:1193: mo // drug pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1195: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK014(pha)003:1196: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK014(pha)003:1197: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK014(pha)003:1198: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1199: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)003:1206: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai m+aa na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1207: gtor ma 'dod yon gyi phung po las 'dod yon
NK014(pha)003:1208: drug gi lha mo dpag tu med pa byung nas
NK014(pha)003:1209: lha rnams dgyes pa bskyed te rang la thim par
NK014(pha)003:1210: bsam mo // bdun pa bdud rtsi gsang nan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1211: bdud rtsi bzed zhal du lan gsum 'phyar zhing /
NK014(pha)003:1213: mi bskyod ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i ro la bsnam du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1215: byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams las bslang ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1216: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad bzhes shing bsnam du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1218: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK014(pha)003:1219: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams bde ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)003:1221: zhen cing chags pa'i mtha' la nyon mongs rno brkam gzir ba yi //
NK014(pha)003:1222: myong byed bde mchog brgyad dang ldan pas thabs kyi sku la smre bar mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1223: 'gro kun tshangs par spyod pa'i byang chub sgo mor lam ston cig /
NK014(pha)003:1224: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa'i tshogs la bka' stsol cig /
NK014(pha)003:1226: zhes dang pos dkyil 'khor pa dgyes pa bskyed /
NK014(pha)003:1227: gnyis pas byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog ma rtogs pa'i nyan thos rnams 'gog pa las bslang /
NK014(pha)003:1228: gsum pas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams gzhan don la bskul zhing gtor ma la'ang spran no //
NK014(pha)003:1229: brgyad pa rak+ta'i mchod pa tshar gsum las /
NK014(pha)003:1232: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK014(pha)003:1233: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)003:1234: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK014(pha)003:1235: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK014(pha)003:1236: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK014(pha)003:1239: ma lus bzhes nas bsnam du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1240: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)003:1245: sh+r+ai ba na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1246: zhes dang po sbrengs pas rak+ta'i dngas ma ye shes
NK014(pha)003:1247: kyi bdud rtsi'i ngo bor sum gcig rol bar bsam
NK014(pha)003:1250: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK014(pha)003:1251: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa yi //
NK014(pha)003:1252: dmar chen bskyil ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK014(pha)003:1254: ma rungs 'dod la ma chags shing //
NK014(pha)003:1255: dam tshig la sdang dgra chen rnams //
NK014(pha)003:1256: thugs rje byang sems ldan pa yis //
NK014(pha)003:1257: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK014(pha)003:1258: dzahmh'u bam ho sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK014(pha)003:1259: sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu dra m+aa ra /
NK014(pha)003:1263: hri da ya pi pa h'u phata /
NK014(pha)003:1264: zhes gnyis pa sbrengs pas rak+ta'i khu ba zhing bcu'i
NK014(pha)003:1265: dgra bgegs kyi ngo bor sum gnyis rol par bsam
NK014(pha)003:1268: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK014(pha)003:1269: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK014(pha)003:1270: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1271: sha rus la sogs za bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:1272: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK014(pha)003:1277: ma h+aa go ro tsa na /
NK014(pha)003:1278: ma h+aa keem ni ri ti /
NK014(pha)003:1279: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK014(pha)003:1280: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha ho /
NK014(pha)003:1286: zhes gsum sbrengs pas rak+ta'i rtsigs ma zhing bcu'i dug
NK014(pha)003:1287: gsum sha khrag rus pa'i dngos por lhag med du
NK014(pha)003:1290: rang gi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK014(pha)003:1292: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK014(pha)003:1293: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK014(pha)003:1294: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa bsregs /
NK014(pha)003:1295: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)003:1297: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK014(pha)003:1298: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK014(pha)003:1299: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK014(pha)003:1300: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK014(pha)003:1302: yab kyi nor bu h'u las rtse lnga pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:1303: rdo rje'i dbyibs can zla bar gyis mtshan //
NK014(pha)003:1304: yum gyi chos 'byung mam las 'dab brgyad kyi //
NK014(pha)003:1305: pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru nyi mar mum gyis mtshan //
NK014(pha)003:1306: yab kyi sa ma ho yis brdas bskul bas //
NK014(pha)003:1307: yum gyi sa ma ya s+t+wam lan btab pa //
NK014(pha)003:1308: yab kyis r+aa ga ya ho'i brda sbyar bas //
NK014(pha)003:1309: yum gyis r+aa ga ya mi brda yis bskul //
NK014(pha)003:1310: dzahmh'u bam hoh b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha ho /
NK014(pha)003:1311: zhes dga' ba bzhi'i rol mos so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su sad par bsam zhing //
NK014(pha)003:1312: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK014(pha)003:1313: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK014(pha)003:1314: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK014(pha)003:1315: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK014(pha)003:1316: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa w+aa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)003:1317: zhes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rjes
NK014(pha)003:1318: su chags pa dang dbyer med pa'i nga rgyal bya'o
NK014(pha)003:1319: // bcu gcig pa 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1321: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK014(pha)003:1322: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK014(pha)003:1324: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK014(pha)003:1325: 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor dag pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:1326: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad bde ba chen por
NK014(pha)003:1327: ro gcig tu gyur par bsams pa ni bla na
NK014(pha)003:1328: med pa dug gsum lam du slong ba'i mchod pa'o
NK014(pha)003:1329: // bcu gnyis pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1340: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK014(pha)003:1341: ston ka'i zla gsum dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK014(pha)003:1342: bcom ldan bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK014(pha)003:1343: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK014(pha)003:1344: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngams pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK014(pha)003:1345: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:1346: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK014(pha)003:1347: bzhes te a la la yis dgyes par mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1348: ces pas bdud dang log 'dren rnams tshar gcod pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:1349: mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba dang dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo la bstod cing bskul ba dang /
NK014(pha)003:1350: chos kyi sgra rnams mtha' yas pa so so'i mos
NK014(pha)003:1351: pa bzhin 'char bar mos la rol mo sna tshogs
NK014(pha)003:1353: bcu gsum pa ye shes glu'i mchod pa gsang ba gsum gyi yon tan dran pas bstod pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1355: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK014(pha)003:1357: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)003:1358: mche ba zang yag za byed che //
NK014(pha)003:1361: rngams pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK014(pha)003:1362: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK014(pha)003:1363: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK014(pha)003:1364: spyugs pa'i mthor rlung g.yeng ba che //
NK014(pha)003:1366: h'u khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK014(pha)003:1367: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK014(pha)003:1369: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK014(pha)003:1372: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK014(pha)003:1375: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che //
NK014(pha)003:1378: bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK014(pha)003:1379: bdud kyi bdud byed bdud rnams 'joms //
NK014(pha)003:1381: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che /
NK014(pha)003:1384: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK014(pha)003:1385: rdo rje chu ste sdud chen po //
NK014(pha)003:1386: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK014(pha)003:1387: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho //
NK014(pha)003:1389: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1393: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1394: dzahmh'u bam hoh pra t+aits+tsha ho /
NK014(pha)003:1395: zhes me tog dor ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)003:1397: spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na /
NK014(pha)003:1398: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK014(pha)003:1399: ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK014(pha)003:1400: kyi bye brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK014(pha)003:1401: chen po he ru ka la sogs pa rigs lnga'i
NK014(pha)003:1402: bde bar gshegs pa rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum gyi
NK014(pha)003:1403: dbyings na rnam par bzhugs pa sems dpa'i tshogs /
NK014(pha)003:1405: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug /
NK014(pha)003:1406: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK014(pha)003:1410: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK014(pha)003:1411: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK014(pha)003:1412: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK014(pha)003:1413: dam tshig gnyen po ma nor bar mnos pa las /
NK014(pha)003:1414: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag dang 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK014(pha)003:1415: lha nye bar ma bsgoms pa /
NK014(pha)003:1416: snying po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK014(pha)003:1417: sbyor ba mang pos bar bskums pa /
NK014(pha)003:1418: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK014(pha)003:1419: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK014(pha)003:1421: dam rdzas lag len rdo ma thogs pa /
NK014(pha)003:1424: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK014(pha)003:1425: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur cing /
NK014(pha)003:1426: sems can gyi spyod pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:1427: khyad par du sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK014(pha)003:1428: khyad par gyi dam tshig gnyen po mngon par mnos pa las /
NK014(pha)003:1429: nyams shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa
NK014(pha)003:1430: thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis
NK014(pha)003:1431: mthol zhing bshags par mchis na /
NK014(pha)003:1432: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gis sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas /
NK014(pha)003:1433: tshangs pa mchog yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1434: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1435: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK014(pha)003:1441: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi bla man chad nas /
NK014(pha)003:1442: dngos grub kyi skal pa dang rigs brgyud gang lags
NK014(pha)003:1443: pa thams cad phyi mar bsdang mi 'tshal bar dus
NK014(pha)003:1444: da lta nyid du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK014(pha)003:1445: rnal 'byor pa la bar du gcod par byed pa /
NK014(pha)003:1453: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK014(pha)003:1454: ltas ngan pa mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams
NK014(pha)003:1455: cad phyir bzlog cing ming tsam yang mi grags par
NK014(pha)003:1456: zhi ba chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK014(pha)003:1457: gal te zhi bas bsgyur du mi btub pa dag
NK014(pha)003:1458: drag po'i phrin las kyis dbang du bsdu ba dang
NK014(pha)003:1460: bsgral zhing spar ba la sogs te /
NK014(pha)003:1461: phrin las drag thabs rnam pa bzhis ji ltar 'dul
NK014(pha)003:1462: bar 'tshams pa bzhin mdzad nas ming tsam yang mi
NK014(pha)003:1464: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du bzhugs pa rnams //
NK014(pha)003:1465: gcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK014(pha)003:1466: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK014(pha)003:1467: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK014(pha)003:1468: gzi ma dngas lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK014(pha)003:1469: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang /
NK014(pha)003:1470: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK014(pha)003:1471: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1475: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK014(pha)003:1476: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK014(pha)003:1477: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK014(pha)003:1478: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)003:1479: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK014(pha)003:1480: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK014(pha)003:1481: srog gi phyir yang mi gtang na //
NK014(pha)003:1482: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlab mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1484: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK014(pha)003:1485: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK014(pha)003:1487: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK014(pha)003:1488: drug pa dzapa la gsum gyi dang po dzapa khang dbye ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1489: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor legs par gsal btab nas /
NK014(pha)003:1490: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzahmh'u ha he phata
NK014(pha)003:1491: b+h+yo ram phata dzah zhes brjod pas dam tshig gi
NK014(pha)003:1492: dkyil 'khor las ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang
NK014(pha)003:1493: brten par bcas pa logs su phye nas /
NK014(pha)003:1494: mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dabs 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par mos pa'o //
NK014(pha)003:1495: gnyis pa dzapa dngos bzla ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1496: bdag bdun gyi lha rnams kyi ye shes sems dpa'i
NK014(pha)003:1497: thugs kar rdo rje'i lte bar nyi ma'i gdan sran
NK014(pha)003:1498: zlum tsam gyi dbus su rigs lnga la h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1499: goo r+ai ma brgyad la ha /
NK014(pha)003:1502: dbang phyug ma rnams la b+h+yo /
NK014(pha)003:1503: de rnams ru lu 'bru brgyad pa'i sngags kyi phreng ba re res bskor bar gsal btab la /
NK014(pha)003:1504: sngags zlos pa'i tshe bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags
NK014(pha)003:1505: kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul du spros pas ye
NK014(pha)003:1506: shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK014(pha)003:1508: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK014(pha)003:1509: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pas bdag la
NK014(pha)003:1510: stsal zhing thim par dmigs pa ste /
NK014(pha)003:1511: bskyed rim chos kyi phyag rgya'i dag rdzogs smin gsum la nges pa rnyed pa /
NK014(pha)003:1512: 'phro 'du las kyi phyag rgya'i sbyang gzhi sbyong byed kyi rnam dag dran pa /
NK014(pha)003:1513: 'da' dka' dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i ngang mnyams pa
NK014(pha)003:1514: lhar snang phyag rgya chen po la gsal brten gyi
NK014(pha)003:1515: tshad brgyad thob par slob bzhin pas /
NK014(pha)003:1516: bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spangs te /
NK014(pha)003:1517: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1518: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:1519: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1520: zhes pas mtshon nas rigs bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)003:1521: gnas yul gyi ma mo sgo skyong dbang phyug ma
NK014(pha)003:1522: rnams so so'i bskyed sngags la ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK014(pha)003:1523: sbyar ba gtso 'khor gyis 'gros dang sbyar bas /
NK014(pha)003:1524: brgya dang nyer gcig bdun sogs rim par bzla zhing /
NK014(pha)003:1525: spyi dzapa ni ru lu nyid la gtso bor bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:1526: deng sang rgyud sde chen po'i ring lugs la 'jug
NK014(pha)003:1527: pa nyung yang gal te smin par slob pa byung
NK014(pha)003:1528: srid na grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa spyi dang
NK014(pha)003:1529: mthun pa nges rdzogs las kyang bshad do //
NK014(pha)003:1530: gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba la gsum las /
NK014(pha)003:1531: dang po gzhi bstod bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1532: h'u dus gsum mi 'gyur rnam shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK014(pha)003:1533: zhe sdang mthar phyin badz+ra he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:1534: dbyings nas rgyas 'debs badz+ra khros ma'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1535: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1536: ma 'gags rang gsal gzugs phung chos kyi sku //
NK014(pha)003:1537: gti mug mthar phyin bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:1538: dbyings nas rmongs sel bud+d+ha khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1539: bud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1540: za byed gter tshogs tshor ba rin 'byung sku //
NK014(pha)003:1541: nga rgyal mtha' phyin rat+na he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:1542: dbyings nas tshe 'phel rat+na khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1543: rat+na he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1544: chags med dag pa 'du shes pad+ma'i sku //
NK014(pha)003:1545: 'dod chags mthar phyin pad+ma he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:1546: dbyings nas rdzogs byed pad+ma khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1547: pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1548: don rnams mthar phyin 'du byed sprul pa'i sku //
NK014(pha)003:1549: phrag dog mthar phyin karma he ru ka /
NK014(pha)003:1550: dbyings nas za byed karma khros pa'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1551: karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1552: 'jig rten bzhad pa'i dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)003:1553: thugs mchog rnam dag ye shes dkar mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1554: thugs rje chen po'i rnal 'byor grogs mdzad ma //
NK014(pha)003:1555: gnas kyi goo r+ai brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1556: yon tan rtags kyi dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK014(pha)003:1557: 'jigs byed rtsal 'phags seng gdong phra men tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1558: thugs rje chen po'i rnal 'byor grogs 'dzad ma //
NK014(pha)003:1559: yul gyi phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1560: phyin ci log bzhi dur khrod gnas bzhi nas //
NK014(pha)003:1561: tshad med bzhi yi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:1562: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK014(pha)003:1563: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1564: lha chen rnams kyi chung ma dbang mo'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1565: 'khor ba'i chos la mnga' brnyes srin mo'i gzugs //
NK014(pha)003:1566: mya ngan 'das pa'i sprul sku mgo brnyan can //
NK014(pha)003:1567: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK014(pha)003:1568: ye shes zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1569: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
NK014(pha)003:1570: khrag 'thung rol pa'i lha tshogs lnga bcu brgyad //
NK014(pha)003:1571: gdod nas ma skyes rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK014(pha)003:1572: tshe rabs sngon nas bsgrubs pa'i 'phro mchis kyi //
NK014(pha)003:1573: da lta nyid du bdag la mngon gyur cig /
NK014(pha)003:1576: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK014(pha)003:1577: ma rig dbang giis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK014(pha)003:1578: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK014(pha)003:1579: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK014(pha)003:1580: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK014(pha)003:1581: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK014(pha)003:1582: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK014(pha)003:1583: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1584: zhes bzlas pas nyes byas rnams bshags /
NK014(pha)003:1585: gsum pa dzapa khang bsdu ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1586: rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)003:1587: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1588: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)003:1589: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK014(pha)003:1590: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh zhes rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang dngos grub bskul ba /
NK014(pha)003:1591: khro la khros pas sogs sngar bzhin byas nas /
NK014(pha)003:1593: zhes pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis med du bstim la /
NK014(pha)003:1594: gsal zhing brtan pa'i phyir yi ge brgya pa'ang bazla'o //
NK014(pha)003:1595: spyi don gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la /
NK014(pha)003:1604: dge ba bsngo ba shis brjod dang dgu'i dang po tshogs mchod la'ang drug gi /
NK014(pha)003:1605: dang po bsang sbyangs byin brlab ni /
NK014(pha)003:1607: dpal chen thugs las ram yam kham //
NK014(pha)003:1609: snang srid bde chen ka p+aa lar //
NK014(pha)003:1610: bcud rnams rigs lnga'i dam rdzas gyur //
NK014(pha)003:1611: +aahmh'u ha ho h+r+aih gnyis pa spyan 'dren ni /
NK014(pha)003:1613: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang dang //
NK014(pha)003:1614: yan lag bdun ldan longs spyod rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:1615: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams nas //
NK014(pha)003:1616: dpal chen dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK014(pha)003:1617: gnas dang nye gnas rnam par gnyis //
NK014(pha)003:1618: yul ni rol pa nye yul rol //
NK014(pha)003:1619: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing dang ni //
NK014(pha)003:1622: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK014(pha)003:1623: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK014(pha)003:1624: oo di ya nar pad+ma brtsegs //
NK014(pha)003:1625: za hor yul na khu byug klong //
NK014(pha)003:1626: seng nge'i yul na sku la rdzogs //
NK014(pha)003:1627: kha che'i yul na he chen rol //
NK014(pha)003:1628: bal po'i yul na ya ma kha //
NK014(pha)003:1629: tho gar yul na gsang chen rol //
NK014(pha)003:1630: li yul 'jig rten mngon rdzogs te //
NK014(pha)003:1631: dur khrod chen po brgyad rnams na //
NK014(pha)003:1632: bzhugs pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dang //
NK014(pha)003:1634: tshogs la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1635: tshogs khang 'di ni sprul pa'i zhing //
NK014(pha)003:1636: tshogs rdzas 'dod yon rol ba'i rgyan //
NK014(pha)003:1637: thabs dang shes rab lcam dral ldan //
NK014(pha)003:1638: rdo rje'i glu gar byin re chags //
NK014(pha)003:1639: cang te'u dril bu bsnyan cing 'khrol //
NK014(pha)003:1640: 'di ni dam tshig mchog gi gnas //
NK014(pha)003:1641: shags dang rtsod pa ku co med //
NK014(pha)003:1642: rig pa brtul zhugs nyams dang ldan //
NK014(pha)003:1643: dam tshig 'di ni dang du bzhes //
NK014(pha)003:1644: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1645: gu ru d+he wa d+aa k+ka d+aa k+ki ni d+harma
NK014(pha)003:1646: p+aa la badz+ra sa ma ya dzah gsum pa tshogs
NK014(pha)003:1649: sangs rgyas dam tshig bla na med //
NK014(pha)003:1650: sha lnga bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK014(pha)003:1651: bza' bca' btung ba phyi yi tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1652: 'dod yon lha mo rnam pa lnga //
NK014(pha)003:1653: dbang po'i longs spyod nang gi tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1654: bde stong ye shes bla na med //
NK014(pha)003:1655: dga' bzhi rnam rol gsang ba'i tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1657: bzhes nas dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1658: ga na tsakra p+au dza ho /
NK014(pha)003:1661: gang zhig 'khrul par gyur pa de nas bzung //
NK014(pha)003:1662: rnam smin lus la rten pa de srid du //
NK014(pha)003:1663: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med nye ba lnga //
NK014(pha)003:1664: lci ba bcu drug log pa brgyad la sogs //
NK014(pha)003:1665: theg pa gsum dang rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK014(pha)003:1666: sdom gsum dam tshig nyams pa mtha' dag kun //
NK014(pha)003:1667: ga na tshogs kyi 'khor lo la brten nas //
NK014(pha)003:1668: 'chab pa med pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK014(pha)003:1669: dag tshangs chen po'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1670: he ru ka'i yig brgya bazla'o //
NK014(pha)003:1672: e las thar med srid pa'i 'brub khung nang //
NK014(pha)003:1673: ma rig 'khrul pas bcings pa bdag lta'i dgra //
NK014(pha)003:1674: ye shes dbyings la bsgrib pa'i gzung 'dzin bgegs //
NK014(pha)003:1675: dag chen ye shes rig pa'i lcags kyus zung //
NK014(pha)003:1676: mnyam par ma bzhag med pa'i zhags pas chings //
NK014(pha)003:1677: lhag mthong lu gu rgyud kyi d+r+wa bas sdoms //
NK014(pha)003:1678: rjes thob 'khrul pa med pa'i dril bus myos //
NK014(pha)003:1679: phung po lnga yi nye bar len pa kun //
NK014(pha)003:1680: bdag med rtogs pa'i mtshon gyis rnam par gtubs //
NK014(pha)003:1681: skye med khros pa'i lha tshogs zhal du stob //
NK014(pha)003:1687: keem narti ta na tsakra p+au tsa kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK014(pha)003:1689: zhing lpags kyi steng du bzhag la /
NK014(pha)003:1690: he ru ka'i dam rgyas kha phru gdab /
NK014(pha)003:1694: dang po phud kyi mi mchod rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1695: dpal chen dkyil 'khor tshogs kyi bdag /
NK014(pha)003:1696: bar du bshags pa mi bgyi rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1697: rnal 'byor ldan la dam tshig gnyan //
NK014(pha)003:1698: tha ma bsgral bstab mi bgyi rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1699: rtogs pas bdag rgyud sngon bsgral phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1700: da lta lhag mas mi mchod rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1701: ma tshogs dbang phyug ging lang+ka //
NK014(pha)003:1702: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sogs //
NK014(pha)003:1703: kun kyang dpal chen sprul pa yin //
NK014(pha)003:1704: lhag ma kha chus mi bran rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1705: dam tshig gcig tu bsre ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1706: 'bangs thog rje yis mi gnan rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1707: ci bcol las la bskul ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1708: rje la 'bangs kyis mi rgol rgyu //
NK014(pha)003:1709: drag shul las thabs myur ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1711: rnam dag rang bzhin zhi ba las //
NK014(pha)003:1712: bcom ldan dpal chen sprul pa ni //
NK014(pha)003:1713: thabs shes zla gsang rol ba las //
NK014(pha)003:1714: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba ste //
NK014(pha)003:1715: khyed cag sngon gyi yal gam can //
NK014(pha)003:1716: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK014(pha)003:1717: legs nyes stong 'dzin tshogs khang nyul //
NK014(pha)003:1718: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul dpag tu med //
NK014(pha)003:1719: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK014(pha)003:1720: dug gsum r+au tra bsgral ba'i tshe //
NK014(pha)003:1721: khas blangs dam bcas dran gyis la //
NK014(pha)003:1722: srin mo'i za lam chen po ru //
NK014(pha)003:1723: pham phabs long la bstan pa srungs //
NK014(pha)003:1724: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1725: gnyis pa thugs dam bskul ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1727: mi gnas ye shes chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK014(pha)003:1728: longs spyod rdzogs pa zhi dang khro ba'i lha //
NK014(pha)003:1729: thugs dam bskul lo 'gro ba'i don la dgongs //
NK014(pha)003:1730: rig pa'i rang bzhin bde gshegs snying po yang //
NK014(pha)003:1731: ma rig 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi lung ma bstan //
NK014(pha)003:1732: sgo lnga'i yul dang rten cing 'brel ba las //
NK014(pha)003:1733: rigs drug rgyud lnga'i gnas su 'khyams pa rnams //
NK014(pha)003:1734: las dang nyon mongs mthu yis gzir ba'i mthu //
NK014(pha)003:1735: phyi rol yul la smin pa'i sdug bsngal dang //
NK014(pha)003:1736: nad mtshon mu ge dgra bgegs 'byung po'i gdon //
NK014(pha)003:1737: 'jigs pa chen po brgyad dang bcu drug kun //
NK014(pha)003:1738: mngon spyod drag po'i rol pas tshar bcad nas //
NK014(pha)003:1739: log rtog dngos por zhen pa'i sems can rnams //
NK014(pha)003:1740: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis 'dul dka' bas //
NK014(pha)003:1741: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1742: gsum pa chad tho bsgrag pa ni /
NK014(pha)003:1744: dus gsum rnam dag kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK014(pha)003:1745: mngon rdzogs ye shes dam pa'i 'og min du //
NK014(pha)003:1746: kun gzhi yid chos dag pa'i ston pa yis //
NK014(pha)003:1747: rang snang rang bzhin med pa'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK014(pha)003:1748: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud rdzogs pa'i yo ga gsum //
NK014(pha)003:1749: brda tshig brjod pa bral bar bstan pa'i tshe //
NK014(pha)003:1750: grags chen gsal ba'i ston pa bcu gnyis dang //
NK014(pha)003:1751: dga' rab dpa' bo gsang 'dzin rdo rje chos //
NK014(pha)003:1752: brda rgyud rig 'dzin grub pa mchog rnams kyis //
NK014(pha)003:1753: ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig pa'i dbang thob bzhin //
NK014(pha)003:1754: tshogs brgyad rang 'grol gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK014(pha)003:1755: 'khrul pa gzhi la dag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1756: de rjes gsang sngags bstan pa byung ba'i tshe //
NK014(pha)003:1757: 'og min dga' ldan ri rab lhun po'i rtse //
NK014(pha)003:1758: lha gnas gsum du grags pa'i gnas mchog dang //
NK014(pha)003:1759: sham+b+ha la dang o rgyan za hor yul //
NK014(pha)003:1760: sing+ga la dang gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtse //
NK014(pha)003:1761: mchod rten chen po bde byed brtsegs pa ru //
NK014(pha)003:1762: rig 'dzin sde snod mtha' dag babs pa'i tshe //
NK014(pha)003:1764: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba thams cad kyis //
NK014(pha)003:1765: gtor ma len zhing legs nyes stangs 'dzin pa'i //
NK014(pha)003:1766: khas blangs dam bca' bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1767: ces bshal chus gtor mar bran te bstan ma skyong ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1769: tshogs dang bka' yi bdag nyid ni //
NK014(pha)003:1770: khrag 'thung rdo rje nam mkha'i yum //
NK014(pha)003:1771: gangs ri can gyi yul lha ni //
NK014(pha)003:1772: bdud dang gnod sbyin sman mo bzhi //
NK014(pha)003:1773: tshur spyon tshur spyon gtor ma long //
NK014(pha)003:1774: rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis dang //
NK014(pha)003:1775: dus sbyor bcu gnyis gnas dag pas //
NK014(pha)003:1776: bal bod mtshams na tshe ring ma //
NK014(pha)003:1777: la stod rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK014(pha)003:1778: gnod sbyin gangs la kun bzang mo //
NK014(pha)003:1780: jo mo gangs rar spyan gcig ma //
NK014(pha)003:1781: byang na mkha' lding klu mo rgyal //
NK014(pha)003:1782: kha rag rda rje khyung btsun ma //
NK014(pha)003:1783: rma chen spom rar drag mo rgyal //
NK014(pha)003:1784: kong btsun de mo bod khams skyong //
NK014(pha)003:1785: 'brog btsan rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK014(pha)003:1786: jo mo nags rgyal g.yar mo bsil //
NK014(pha)003:1787: dbus na rdo rje thu le sman //
NK014(pha)003:1788: kun kyang pad+ma'i bka' nyan te //
NK014(pha)003:1789: dam la gnas shing rigs la 'go //
NK014(pha)003:1790: tha tshig bzhin du gtor ma longs //
NK014(pha)003:1793: 'gong po spun dgu'i nad dal srungs //
NK014(pha)003:1794: rtag chad thar par 'khrul pa yi //
NK014(pha)003:1795: 'jig tshogs lta ba dbu mar bzlog /
NK014(pha)003:1796: bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis kyi //
NK014(pha)003:1797: bstan pa rgyas pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK014(pha)003:1803: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1804: gtor gzhong ri rab tu bsam pa kha sbub la /
NK014(pha)003:1806: dam sri bya ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK014(pha)003:1807: 'gro ba yongs kyi rgyud la rgol //
NK014(pha)003:1808: byang chub sems kyi brtul zhugs bros //
NK014(pha)003:1809: mnan no stong chen 'og tu mnan //
NK014(pha)003:1810: gtad do chu srin gre bar gtad //
NK014(pha)003:1811: bsgyur ro gshin rje'i kha ru bsgyur //
NK014(pha)003:1812: bsreg go ye shes me yis bsreg /
NK014(pha)003:1813: bdag tu blta ba ma zhig bar //
NK014(pha)003:1814: bskal pa zhig kyang mi gtong ngo //
NK014(pha)003:1816: bzhi pa dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK014(pha)003:1818: byin rlabs kun gyi rtsa ba bla ma ni //
NK014(pha)003:1819: dngos grub stsol phyir dpal chen rol pa'i lha //
NK014(pha)003:1820: rnam thar sgo gsum thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK014(pha)003:1821: rang bzhin yongs grub byang chub sems kyi dngos //
NK014(pha)003:1822: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1823: sa bcu lam lnga dbang bcu phyi nang gnyis //
NK014(pha)003:1824: rig 'dzin bzhi dang sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NK014(pha)003:1825: grub chen brgyad dang phrin las rnam pa bzhi //
NK014(pha)003:1826: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin glo bur sgrib pa gnyis //
NK014(pha)003:1827: kun gzhi'i khams la bag la nyal gyi tshul //
NK014(pha)003:1828: shin tu rnam dag rnam kun mchog ldan gyi //
NK014(pha)003:1829: dngos grub dam pa deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)003:1833: nirma k+aa ya tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la h'u /
NK014(pha)003:1834: zhes sgrub rdzas rnams gnas gsum du gtug cing myong /
NK014(pha)003:1835: slar yang gtang rag gi mchod bstod byas la /
NK014(pha)003:1838: sngags kyi dngos grub ma lus pa //
NK014(pha)003:1839: dam tshig nyid la brten gyur kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1840: rmongs dang ma rig nyon mongs pas //
NK014(pha)003:1841: zil gyis non pa bdag cag ni //
NK014(pha)003:1842: nyes pa du ma'i snod lags te //
NK014(pha)003:1843: mgon po thugs rje che rnams kyi //
NK014(pha)003:1844: thugs la khro ba mi mngas yang //
NK014(pha)003:1845: legs nyes stangs 'dzin bdag po rnams //
NK014(pha)003:1846: skyon mthong tsam na chad pa gcod //
NK014(pha)003:1847: 'gal zhing nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK014(pha)003:1848: mthol lo bshags so tshangs par stsol //
NK014(pha)003:1849: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyi snying nas bshags par bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:1852: snod bcud lha dang gzhal yas su //
NK014(pha)003:1853: shar ba dag pa'i snod bcud kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1854: rten nyid brten pa lha rnams kyang //
NK014(pha)003:1855: gtso bo la thim de yang h'u //
NK014(pha)003:1856: zhabs kyu nas bzung n+aa da'i bar //
NK014(pha)003:1857: rim yal gdod ma'i gshis su +aah zhes mnyam par bzhag /
NK014(pha)003:1858: bdun pa spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK014(pha)003:1859: slar yang rig pa byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)003:1860: rjes thob gnyug ma'i he ru kah phyag rgya gcig pa'i gnas gsum du //
NK014(pha)003:1861: yi ges mtshan pas rnam rtog srungs //
NK014(pha)003:1864: yi ge brgya pas brtan par bya /
NK014(pha)003:1867: snang grags rig pa dkyil 'khor gsum gyi ngang //
NK014(pha)003:1868: bsod nams ye shes rim gnyis rnal 'byor tshogs //
NK014(pha)003:1869: mi gnas ye shes mya ngan 'das par bsngo //
NK014(pha)003:1870: kun kyang dpal chen go 'phar thob par shog /
NK014(pha)003:1874: gdod ma'i mgon po rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho //
NK014(pha)003:1875: sku snga lhun rdzogs sprul pa'i zhing khams la //
NK014(pha)003:1876: bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong rtsa byon pa yi //
NK014(pha)003:1877: sgron ma'i bskal pa bzang po'i bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)003:1878: stong gsum mi mjed rdo rje thegs pa'i zhing //
NK014(pha)003:1879: 'phur 'gro'i bstan pa 'byung gnas o rgyan yul //
NK014(pha)003:1880: gangs ri'i khrod du 'bod pa khri srong rje'i //
NK014(pha)003:1881: thugs bskyed bstan pa mtha' rgyas bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)003:1882: 'dzam gling sa yi lte ba rdo rje'i gdan //
NK014(pha)003:1883: pan grub chos rgyal 'dzom pa chos 'khor gsum //
NK014(pha)003:1884: mdo sngags bstan pa dar ba gangs can ljongs //
NK014(pha)003:1885: rgyal bstan yun du gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)003:1887: bsngo smon gyis mtha' rgyas par bya'o //
NK014(pha)003:1888: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bsgrub pa'i thabs //
NK014(pha)003:1889: rgya gzhung rnams ni brjod byed nyung la dam //
NK014(pha)003:1890: dpal ldan zur pa'i gzhung lugs chu lhar phyogs //
NK014(pha)003:1891: don la g.yel dang byin rlabs zhud pa'i tshe //
NK014(pha)003:1892: 'bab chu'i rgyun ltar bklags pas don grub bsdebs //
NK014(pha)003:1893: rgyal ba'i chos 'khor gsum gyi 'bras bu'i don //
NK014(pha)003:1894: 'og min chen po thog mtha' med dus nas //
NK014(pha)003:1895: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa rig 'dzin brdas brgyud pa //
NK014(pha)003:1896: lung bstan rdo rje'i chos char chen po nyid //
NK014(pha)003:1897: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu dang phyag rgya bzhi'i //
NK014(pha)003:1898: chings kyis skye gnas bzhi yi gnas sbyor zhing //
NK014(pha)003:1899: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi'i go 'phang la sbyor ba //
NK014(pha)003:1900: rdo rje'i sde snod las gzhan ltar snang ches //
NK014(pha)003:1901: nyang smad sa yi thig le rgyal byed tshal //
NK014(pha)003:1902: theg pa mchog gi gling de sgra dang don //
NK014(pha)003:1903: mtshungs par basngagasa pa'i byed po 'di nyid phyir //
NK014(pha)003:1904: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyin byed 'bar gyur cig /
